    <title type="html"><![CDATA[How to install sbt on Fedora 18]]></title>
    <link href="http://gHorHe.github.com/blog/2013/02/19/how-to-install-sbt-on-fedora-18/"/>
    <updated>2013-02-19T01:21:00+07:00</updated>
